title: [1508428454] Timings and Temperatures for Perfect Roast Turkey - Gordon Ramsay
description:
From Christmas with Gordon (2010.) All temperatures are in Celsius/Centigrade. If you are in the USA: 220°C is 420°F and 180°C is 350°F.
